  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK266">
<l>tavañceyvār taṅkarumañ ceyvārmaṟ ṟallā</l>
<l>ravañceyvā rācaiyiṟ paṭṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those discharge their duty who perform austerities; all others accomplish their own destruction, through the entanglement of the desire (of riches and sensual pleasure).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
